Assigning a completely new array to a `@tracked` property is always safe and triggers a re-render. This is the cleanest approach when you want to replace all data at once, such as after an API response or switching between match formats.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component';
import { tracked } from '@glimmer/tracking';
