`TrackedObject` wraps a plain object so that direct property mutations become reactive. Import from `tracked-built-ins`. Unlike a plain `@tracked` object, you can do `this.stats.runs += 1` directly without replacing the whole object. This is ideal for objects with many independently-updated fields.

