The `{{#if}}` block re-evaluates whenever the `@tracked` boolean changes. The `{{else}}` block is rendered when the value is falsy. Using `@tracked` with `{{if}}` is the standard pattern for conditional rendering in Glimmer — the UI stays in sync automatically.

```gjs
import Component from '@glimmer/component';
