Without `@tracked`, a plain class field is invisible to Glimmer's reactivity system. The value updates in memory, but Glimmer never schedules a re-render because it has no subscription to the field. Add `@tracked` to every property whose changes should be reflected in the template.

```gjs
// ❌ WRONG
