Using the lowercase HTML attribute `onclick=` sets a raw DOM event attribute which does not integrate with Ember's event system and will pass the raw `Event` object in unexpected ways. The `{{on}}` modifier is the correct Glimmer/Ember approach — it properly adds an `addEventListener` and works seamlessly with `@action` methods.

```gjs
