`this.set()` is part of the classic Ember Object model (`@ember/object`). Glimmer components extend `@glimmer/component` and do not inherit `this.set()`. Reactivity is handled by `@tracked` fields and plain JavaScript assignment. Attempting to call `this.set()` will throw a `TypeError: this.set is not a function` error at runtime.

