`@tracked` registers each decorated property in Glimmer's reactive tag system, allocating tracking infrastructure that is checked on every render cycle. For values that are set once at class initialization and never mutated, this infrastructure is pure waste. Use plain class fields for constants and reserve `@tracked` exclusively for state that the component will modify after initial render.

